name: A Glimpse Beyond Space & Time - of death untranscendable and inescapable
description:
Digital Video, 2400 x 2400 px, 46 seconds, 60 fps, no sound. 

Created February 10, 2022. 

Generative artwork created procedurally in Photoshop using custom macros and scripts. Incorporates elements of the Content Aware Feedback technique developed by 2.0 Organics.  Post processing in After Effects.
